				<li id="comment-1059">
					<article>
						<p>Yes. Default English (if you&#8217;re not logged in), but you can pick your language.</p>
<p>Pretty much a standard way of localizing application, which works fine if you expect your tool to be used by a fairly closed groups of people (like friends and family). </p>
<p>However, it doesn&#8217;t work that great where social relationships are more open (it&#8217;s the groups part of Marela that worries me).</p>
